---
title: Rustic Italian Chicken Tacos with Creamy Parmesan Dressing
description: For our latest invention, you start with flavourful herbed chicken, add crisp lettuce and a creamy Parmesan dressing and pop the whole thing in soft flour tortillas. It's just like a chicken Caesar salad, but our version is extra filling and you can use your hands to enjoy it. We say it's win-win!
